            <h2 class="archive__item-title">Who am I?</h2>
          

          
            <div class="archive__item-excerpt">
              <p>My name is <strong>Carlos F. A. Gomes</strong>.  I’m a scientist, psychologist (B.S., M.A., and Ph.D.), math modeler (stochastic processes), programmer, statistician, magic the gathering player, free knowledge supporter, single-board computer fanatic, and electronics hobbyist.  My beverage of choice is <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mat%C3%A9_(drink)"><em>chimarrão</em></a> (<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gaucho"><em>gaúcho</em></a>-style) but you’ll often find me drinking black tea with milk, too.</p>

